{"tid":1297634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂兒登仔 我係林鄭 多謝你哋今晚玩鳩自己人","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:40:17.000Z","uid":46151,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"66288119e0353edee6a4ea15a7aeffc34cfb83af","tid":1297634,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"你哋班傻西 我支私兵有自己電台㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋唔係覺得兒登廿幾萬會員 一條針都冇下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋開兩個監控鏡頭出嚟 成個金鐘睇曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啊肥仔聰同我講 個post出咗五分鐘佢哋就知係流料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋班傻仔呃咗啲自己友同埋啲記者出嚟<br />\n我代表警察多謝你哋添啊<br />\n<br />\n估唔到幾個戇鳩仔就可以分化曬你哋自己人<br />\n仲有幾千正評幾千回覆<br />\n簡簡單單就消耗曬啲士氣同信任<br />\n如果下次你哋話要人冇人出 就抵鳩你哋死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n笑就笑完 你班傻仔準備聽我聽日開記招9up啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dff00fcc563e7dc27500015536fb8655e60e91c","tid":1297634,"uid":46151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:15:09.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為淨係笑都有排笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3b0c3c51c378e6a55c9a68cffe735ee25f37c7","tid":1297634,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"你哋班傻鳩駁唔駁到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046b025772a395f7249739b4c76cb7